thread.title: Timothy Hancock
thread.title_full: Store DJ reviewed by Timothy Hancock

author: Timothy Hancock
title: Timothy Hancock
text:
I ordered a mixing desk from store dj and was shocked to receive a phone call checking my details and checking my order almost instantly!
The guys there are so professional it's an old school service model that will always surpass others
Well done love the product and brilliant customer service!
